<emphasis box="[174,232,1739,1764]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="200">niger</emphasis>
— black, dark, and 
<emphasis box="[466,536,1739,1764]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="200">tarsus</emphasis>
.
</paragraph>
